---
import MainLayout from '../../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import TedaviDoktorlari from '../../../components/TedaviDoktorlari.astro';

// SEO Title and Description
const pageTitle = "Pedodontics (Pediatric Dentistry) | Yuceler A+ Clinic";
const pageDescription = "Fearless, painless cavity treatment, fluoride application, and preventive medicine services with our expert pediatric dentist (pedodontist) staff in Silivri and Catalca.";
---

<MainLayout title={pageTitle}>
  
  <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/images/pedodonti-banner.webp');"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-klinik-koyu/95 via-klinik-koyu/60 to-transparent z-0"></div> 
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl relative z-10 flex flex-col items-start text-left">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-block bg-klinik-yesil text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase">Child Friendly Clinic</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight text-white drop-shadow-2xl">
          Fun and Fearless <br/><span class="text-klinik-yesil">Pediatric Dentistry</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-100 mb-10 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed drop-shadow-lg">
          From infancy to youth, we protect our children's oral and dental health, and with our special approaches, we help them overcome their fear of the dentist.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-start">
        
        <div class="w-full lg:w-2/3 prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-6">What is Pedodontics?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            <strong>Pedodontics</strong> is the specialty branch of dentistry that undertakes the healthy protection of primary and permanent teeth of children aged 0-14, the tracking of their development, and the treatment of problems caused by decay or trauma in these teeth.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Unfortunately, the misconception among the public that "it's a milk tooth, it will fall out anyway" is very common. However, primary teeth not only provide the child with proper nutrition and speech; they also <strong>guide and hold space for the permanent teeth that will come underneath.</strong> Primary teeth lost at an early age lead to serious orthodontic (requiring braces) problems in the future.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border-l-4 border-klinik-yesil mb-10">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-4">Preventive Treatments Applied in Our Clinic</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 font-medium">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Fissure Sealant (Protective Filling):</strong> It is the process of closing the deep pits on the chewing surfaces of the back teeth to prevent the accumulation of food residues and decay.</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Fluoride Application:</strong> It is a gel application that strengthens the tooth enamel and increases its resistance to acids, protecting the teeth against decay like armor.</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Primary Tooth Filling and Root Canal Treatment:</strong> It ensures that decaying milk teeth are treated without pain and kept in the mouth until the age of falling out.</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Space Maintainers:</strong> These are special appliances made to preserve the space of the permanent tooth coming from below in place of primary teeth that had to be extracted early.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-6">End to Dentist Fear in Children</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-klinik-koyu text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-2">Tell - Show - Do Method</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">We do not start the procedure immediately when our children sit in the dentist's chair. First, we introduce the tools like toys, show how they work, and start the treatment after gaining their trust.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-klinik-koyu text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-2">Completely Painless Treatments</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">We complete the procedures without causing any pain or ache with special fruit-flavored topical (rub-on) anesthetics and modern devices with very fine tips.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-klinik-koyu text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-2">Sedation and General Anesthesia</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">For our children who cannot communicate, are very young, have severe phobias, or have special needs, we safely perform all their treatments in a single session while asleep, accompanied by an anesthesiologist.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/3 sticky top-32">
          <img src="/images/pedodonti-kutu.webp" alt="Pediatric Dentist Examination" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-t-2xl shadow-sm" />
          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 p-8 rounded-b-2xl shadow-xl">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-4">Healthy Smiles of the Future</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6 text-sm">Make an appointment with our experts so that your child's first dentist experience is trauma-free and fun.</p>
            
            <a href="https://wa.me/902124000013" target="_blank" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-[#25D366] text-white font-bold py-4 px-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-green-600 transition-colors mb-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12.031 21.033c-1.56 0-3.084-.42-4.42-1.216l-.317-.189-3.284.861.876-3.203-.207-.331a9.022 9.022 0 0 1-1.378-4.755C3.301 7.155 7.215 3.24 12.031 3.24c2.33 0 4.519.907 6.166 2.555 1.648 1.648 2.556 3.837 2.556 6.167 0 4.914-3.915 8.829-8.73 8.829z" /></svg>
              Get Info via WhatsApp
            </a>
            <a href="tel:+902124000013" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-klinik-koyu text-white font-bold py-4 px-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-black transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" /></svg>
              Call Clinic: +90 212 400 00 13
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <TedaviDoktorlari tedavi="pedodonti" />

  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-100 pb-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-klinik-koyu mb-4">Frequently Asked <span class="text-klinik-yesil">Questions</span></h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">What parents wonder most about pediatric dentistry.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg text-klinik-koyu">
            When should my child's first dentist examination be?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">The World Health Organization and pediatric dentists recommend that the first examination be performed after the child's first milk tooth appears in the mouth (between approximately 6 months and 1 year of age). This examination is of vital importance to inform the family about nutrition and brushing and to prevent future decays.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg text-klinik-koyu">
            Does a filling or root canal treatment on primary teeth damage the tooth?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">Absolutely not. On the contrary, if decayed milk teeth are not treated, the inflammation can damage the enamel of the permanent tooth coming from below. The treated milk tooth continues its duty healthily in the child's mouth until the permanent tooth erupts.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg text-klinik-koyu">
            Is fluoride application harmful to children?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">No, it is not harmful. It has been scientifically proven that superficial fluoride applied in the right dose under the supervision of a physician in a clinical setting is the safest and most effective known method for preventing tooth decay. It is a standard preventive treatment all over the world.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="bg-klinik-koyu text-white py-12 border-t-4 border-klinik-turuncu mt-auto">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h3 class="text-klinik-turuncu font-bold text-lg mb-3">Legal Notice</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          This website has been prepared solely for the purpose of informing patients, in full compliance with the Ministry of Health regulations.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-sm text-gray-400 text-left md:text-right">
        <p class="mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Dental Implant Clinic A Plus</p>
        <p class="mb-1">Call Center: <span class="text-klinik-turuncu">+90 212 400 00 13</span></p>
        <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-gray-800 rounded-lg inline-block text-left border border-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-1 text-xs">Last Updated: <span class="text-white font-bold">21.02.2026</span></p>
          <p class="text-xs">Editor: <a href="mailto:info@dentalimplanttrakya.com" class="text-klinik-turuncu hover:underline">info@dentalimplanttrakya.com</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <div class="h-16 md:hidden block"></div>

</MainLayout>